## Différences clés Gmail vs Outlook

| Aspect | Gmail | Outlook |
|---|---|---|
| Lib auth | `google-auth-oauthlib` (Flow) | `requests` direct (token endpoint) |
| Serialisation token | `pickle` base64 | JSON texte |
| Stockage DB | `profile.google_token_pickle` | `oauth_tokens (provider='microsoft', service='mail')` |
| Credentials source | `var/credentials.json` | env vars `AZUR_*` |
| API messages | `googleapis` SDK | `https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/me/messages` |
| Refresh | `creds.refresh(Request())` | POST token endpoint `grant_type=refresh_token` |
| Scopes email | `gmail.send`, `gmail.readonly`, `drive`, `spreadsheets` | `Mail.Read`, `Mail.Send`, `offline_access` |

